		<title>Getting a Better Start: Serve and Explore</title>
		<link>http://facio.com/blog/2013/02/getting-a-better-start-serve-and-explore/</link>
		<comments>http://facio.com/blog/2013/02/getting-a-better-start-serve-and-explore/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 19 Feb 2013 12:00:57 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Dirk]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
